The omissions of the lists themselves also merit a word. We have seen that houses of Friars are included only by Boston‚ and only four by him. It will be noticed that neither of the Universities and no College is men- tioned. Of Cathedrals‚ York, Lichfield, and the four Welsh ones seem to be the only omissions, Other Collegiate churches and non-monastic establishments are absent, unless Bakewell and the Hospitals of Lincoln are exceptions.
